WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
<v Narrator>Welcome to RestoreAssist. This is your complete dashboard overview.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:12.000
<v Narrator>The top navigation bar gives you quick access to Inspections, Reports, Team, and Settings.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:20.000
<v Narrator>The main dashboard shows your active jobs, pending claims, and recent activity at a glance.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:28.000
<v Narrator>Click New Inspection to start documenting a new job from anywhere.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:35.000
<v Narrator>Your Analytics panel tracks team performance, revenue, and claim outcomes over time.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.000
<v Narrator>Everything you need is one click away.
